PART 5 — AI ASSISTANT, REPORTS, NOTIFICATIONS & ADMINISTRATION UI DESIGN
107. AI Assistant Module Overview
107.1 Purpose
The AI Assistant is the intelligent interface of the AI Threat Hunting & Threat Intelligence Agent. It enables cybersecurity professionals to interact with the platform using natural language, allowing them to investigate vulnerabilities, analyze Indicators of Compromise (IOCs), review malware behavior, generate detection rules, and produce executive summaries.
The interface is designed to make complex cybersecurity information easier to understand while maintaining transparency through explainable AI, supporting references, and confidence indicators.

Objectives
The AI Assistant enables users to:
Ask cybersecurity questions
Explain vulnerabilities
Analyze malware
Investigate phishing attacks
Search historical intelligence
Generate reports
Create Sigma/YARA/Snort rules
Produce mitigation recommendations
Summarize threat intelligence
Continue previous investigations
