137. Part 5 Summary
This section defines the user experience for the AI Assistant, report generation, notifications, user profile, settings, and administration modules. The interfaces emphasize explainable AI, efficient reporting, responsive notifications, and secure system management while maintaining consistency with the overall design system. Together, these modules support analysts, administrators, and executives in completing investigations, managing the platform, and making informed security decisions through a unified, enterprise-grade user experience.
