UI/UX DESIGN DOCUMENT
AI Threat Hunting & Threat Intelligence Agent
PART 6 — RESPONSIVE DESIGN, ACCESSIBILITY, UX STANDARDS, DESIGN QA & FUTURE ROADMAP
138. Responsive Design Strategy
138.1 Overview
The AI Threat Hunting & Threat Intelligence Agent is designed as a responsive enterprise web application that provides an optimized experience across desktop, laptop, tablet, and mobile devices. The interface automatically adapts to different screen sizes while preserving usability, readability, and functionality.
The primary target environment is a Security Operations Center (SOC), where analysts typically use dual-monitor desktop workstations. However, executives and administrators can also access the platform from tablets and mobile devices.

Responsive Objectives
The responsive design aims to:
Maintain layout consistency
Optimize screen utilization
Reduce scrolling
Preserve readability
Support touch interactions
Ensure accessibility
Improve mobile usability
